stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Viewing: mount()
    
    Viewing --> Creating: createCampus()
    Viewing --> Editing: updateCampus(id)
    
    Creating --> ModalOpen: showCampusModel()
    Editing --> ModalOpen: showCampusModel()
    
    ModalOpen --> Validating: save()
    ModalOpen --> Viewing: Cancel
    
    Validating --> Saving: Validation Success
    Validating --> ModalOpen: Validation Failed
    
    Saving --> Viewing: Success Toast
    
    Viewing --> Sorting: Change sortBy
    Sorting --> Viewing: Refresh Table
    
    note right of ModalOpen
        - campusModal = true
        - Reset error bag
        - Initialize form fields
        - Switch between language tabs
    end note
    
    note right of Saving
        - Fill campus model
        - Sync institutes
        - Save to database
    end note
    
    note right of Viewing
        - Display campuses table
        - Show institutes badges
        - Sort by name/direction
    end note
